## சென்னைப் பல்கலைக்கழகத் தமிழ்ப் பேரகராதி
ஆறாரச்சக்கரம்
--
- āṟāra-c-cakkaram
- n. <</>id.+āra+cakra.
- Stanza of four lines so composed that it can be written in the form of a wheel with six spokes, some of the letters being repeated in readings as one goes on reading the lines from spoke to spoke, a variety of cakkara-pantam;
- மிறைக்கவியுள் ஒன்று (மாறன.282, உரை.)